he old stronghold.\n\n[[Image:Stary Plzenec CZ Masaryk Square pano from S 0605.jpg|thumb|none|350px|Masaryk Square with church of St John The Baptist (left) and Town Hall (right).]]\n\n==Notable people==\n* [[Filip J\u00edcha]] (born 1982), handballer\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Plze\u0148-City District}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Stary Plzenec}}\n[[Category:Cities and towns in the Czech Republic]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Plze\u0148-South District]]\n\n\n{{Plze\u0148-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star%C3%BD_Plzenec"}
